Royal Knight
The Royal Knights are the armored defenders of the European kingdoms, sworn
to protect their liege and uphold a code of honor that has survived the coming
of the Rifts. They are comparable to Cyber-Knights in discipline but bound by
feudal obligation rather than independent wandering.

Royal Knights choose from Physical, Military, Weapons, and Technical skill
categories. They are trained in mounted combat, melee weapons, and the
protocols of European noble society.

Attribute requirements: IQ 9, PS 12, PE 12.
Starting equipment: European plate armor or equivalent MDC armor, a longsword
or vibro-blade, shield, a warhorse or equivalent mount, and a sworn service
to a recognized European noble house.
